Content:
SASS can give you the same result:<p><pre><code>    %red 
      color: #f00
    %blue
      color: #00f
    header
      @extend %red
    div
      @extend %blue
    #foo
      @extend %red
    p
      @extend %red
</code></pre>
gets processed into<p><pre><code>    header, #foo, p {
        color: #F00;
    }
    div {
        color: #00F;
    }
</code></pre>
codepen sample: <a href=\http://cdpn.io/JoHAv" rel="nofollow">http://cdpn.io/JoHAv</a>"
